{
  "id": "RAW_b5eeea68",
  "title": "【原理到实战】实验异质性分析",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&mid=2247501517&idx=1&sn=cf25b6e5fa13100bba6d84781515e2e1",
  "date": "2025-12-10 10:18:00",
  "author": "京东技术",
  "siteName": "京东技术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"143788\" data-color=\"e3fcff\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:15px;\">\n     <div data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;background-color: transparent;\">\n      <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"134666\">\n       <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;text-align: center;\">\n        <div hm_fix=\"410:186\" style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n         <p data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"padding:4px 1em;font-size:16px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">本文导读</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在实验数据分析的场景中，经常会遇到分析同样的处理效果在不同的用户群体上是否存在显著差异的问题，此时我们可以利用实验异质性的分析方法，对实验结果进行精细化分析，辅助挖掘结果背后的业务逻辑，帮助业务迭代优化。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <p style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么是实验的异质性</span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;text-wrap:wrap;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:20px;line-height:1.6em;outline:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mizmpvjum8f\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizmpvkgdll\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">什么是异质性</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当我们看到如下实验平台指标结果时</span></span></p>\n  <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:235px;\">\n   <tbody>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"117\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">实验分组</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"118\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">指标值</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"117\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对照组</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"118\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">100</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"117\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实验组</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"118\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">99.96</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"117\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相对差异</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"118\">\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">-0.04%</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在进行分析前，可能我们的第一直觉是这样的</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030722\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.21296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"123\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0c73752&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenFibnDvcRDaJl7ykmDdJrarMDn4iaGS24f9f3RHhy032pNyyK1pHrB9Z8MhB9WBVajLm3WJvttia1ZunA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经过异质性分析后，可能会发现实际情况是这样的</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030724\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.20555555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"119\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=638cfb1a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenFibnDvcRDaJl7ykmDdJrarMDeObwCoTFwLYchrN8vTsE7EwIibpRKwVcwLwAh9DU918VeKhlDSqc70w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;text-wrap:wrap;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:20px;line-height:1.6em;outline:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mizmqb2440s\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizmqb2s1zj1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">概念解析与定义</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一般来讲，HTE的全称为Heterogeneous Treatment Effects，即异质处理效应，意为实验中同一个treatment对不同的实验样本，得到的策略效果可能是不一样的。另外还有一些重要的概念需要大家理解：</span></span></p>\n  <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;min-width:428px;\">\n   <tbody>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"85\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">英文简称</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"115\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">英文全称</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"103\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">中文译名</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"100\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">含义</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">公式</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"85\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ATE</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"115\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Average Treatment Effect</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"103\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">平均处理效应</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"100\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">所有实验对象的平均实验效果</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030742\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.18689320388349515\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"412\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"inline\" data-backw=\"154\" data-backh=\"29\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3fcf0ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAe1MJmaQUqFLtoxz6IDbx1VYJITEpWJQeKjRVCWyxetbJo1Av9PbRfaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"85\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">CATE</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"115\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Conditional Average Treatment Effect</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"103\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">条件平均处理效应</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"100\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">满足一定条件的实验对象的平均实验效果</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030743\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.11929824561403508\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"570\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"inline\" data-backw=\"154\" data-backh=\"18\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db7a52e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAe72WByZia6bImr8paK0vzEb2zBEpwYMDCoj4jznOeAFHxaWdiaCc1H9uA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"85\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ITE</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"115\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Individual Treatment Effect</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"103\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个体处理效应</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td data-colwidth=\"100\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">某个实验对象的实验效果</span></span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030744\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.10855263157894737\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"608\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"inline\" data-backw=\"154\" data-backh=\"17\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3347e134&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAe4LUORmpia4jv5K72vhiaujHERNKTePkiboGhLu93B8YlsyQFrhtMLwY8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">* 此处采用Donald Rubin提出的潜在因果框架（Potencial outcome）来对实验效果进行统计公式上的描述 [1]</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">* 由于业内并没有统一的定义，HTE、CATE、ITE概念在一定程度上会有混用的情况，读者需要参考描述以及上下文综合判断名词的含义</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mizmr06oy2f\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizmr07aquy\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">异质性分析对于业务的意义</span></span></h3>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">了解策略对于</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同用户的不同效果，协助挖掘背后的业务逻辑，辅助迭代、进行新一轮的实验</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尝试寻找策略最优子人群，让整体无效的策略，有机会进行部分先推全；反之依然，让部分负向的策略，减少损失</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对实验结果建模后预测，对线上提供动态的最优人群支持</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据实验平台数据科学团队测算，以京东零售某产品线下6月运行中的实验为例，仅23%左右的实验没有在实验人群视角发现异质性</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <p style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">异质性分析方法概述</span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;text-wrap:wrap;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:20px;line-height:1.6em;outline:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mizmter8lfv\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizmterx14w4\">异质性分析的维度选择</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1. 对于分流单元的维度X，当X满足以下条件时，可以作为异质性的维度进行后续分析。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\">T⊥X<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，即分析维度与实验分流无关 (Unconfoundedness)</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">分析工具化的常见简化方式：对于一个分流ID，选取他在首次进入实验前一天的标签取值</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">简单推导：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030725\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.2118421052631579\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"760\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"557\" data-backh=\"118\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=92b9b240&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAeN7UmHAUeDVnP4yc8FPbz7ibcDILtJ2Ssjk6Mia3BczqOBZGNBdfmbDUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030726\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.152\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"625\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"557\" data-backh=\"85\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aea57b7a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAeQpAhxIicEsicibdzVr7j6teoX9cksDLibj5HNldvMxPmSqAJV8MGodacsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2. 异质性分析的维度分析bad case举例</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030727\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.793584379358438\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"717\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"459\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36168a55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAeqJ2okyqGzD8xmVZyWAPaYlzhv7bP7ibThekOKtmj3gcY385CzfxicOeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D7\"></p>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;text-wrap:wrap;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:20px;line-height:1.6em;outline:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mizmx1jbfro\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizmx1jy119v\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">异质性分析的方法选择</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030728\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.3816901408450704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"710\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"799\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=550ffb24&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAeo72oyibP1aB9Cpe4Wwdia5FHWnsYUOKg64pLXtjfm1jtxt6cxj8UibWtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D8\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <p style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验CATE下钻探索工具MVP版逻辑介绍</span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验平台数据科学团队已经产出python工具包，可以半自动化的利用6行代码实现平台上实验异质性的探索分析，可以实现以下功能</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">1.通过填写YAML配置，自动生成实验分析SQL，并执行取数，目前包括</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动获取试金石实验分流信息</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动获取试金石实验指标信息</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">解</span></span><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">析实验CATE研究使用的用户标签表</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动生成所有数据源的关联关系</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 为实验CATE研究提供自动化工具，目前包括</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动化生成实验目标指标的CATE差异最大化子人群</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提供调参接口，高级用户可自定义模型参数</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提供可视化的模型结果输出，高级用户可根据输出调节模型表现</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">3. 为实验的下钻分析提供探索、分析功能，目前包括</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">CATE人群的实验效果统计检验</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">CATE人群的多指标拆解</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">CATE人群的特征描述</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <p style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">04</span></strong></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验异质性分析show case</span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">某真实实验case的CATE结果分析，此项目整体实验指标为负向不显著，但通过运行分析工具后发现，有两类子人群分别具有正向和负向的显著效果。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100030735\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.3453703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"557\" data-backh=\"193\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41014e3e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenF94iagRUUVhj82SzxEgocDAex4zdIRgaCeicqbTkAoNS3lgI8n0Kqx0bD5bUicdj75vWHX90DQEhIBmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D9\"></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mizn7cl51rmq\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizn7cluloh\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于这些子人群，我们发现他们的用户画像具备不同的特征，在业务漏斗的实验结果也不一致，那么下次对频道再次进行迭代时，产品经理可以有针对性的对负向人群的体验进行优化。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细阐述了实验异质性分析的原理、业务意义及在京东零售的实践，通过识别不同用户群体的差异化实验效果，辅助业务进行精细化迭代优化。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细阐述了实验异质性分析的原理、业务意义及在京东零售的实践，通过识别不同用户群体的差异化实验效果，辅助业务进行精细化迭代优化。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了实验异质性分析（HTE）在 A/B 实验数据分析中的重要作用。首先，通过直观示例解释了异质性概念，并明确了平均处理效应（ATE）、条件平均处理效应（CATE）和个体处理效应（ITE）的定义。接着，强调了异质性分析对于业务的深远意义，包括挖掘业务逻辑、寻找最优子人群以及提供动态最优人群支持。文章还介绍了异质性分析的维度选择原则（T⊥X）和常见方法概述。最后，以京东零售的实践为例，展示了其团队开发的 Python 工具包如何实现 CATE 下钻探索，并提供了一个真实实验案例，说明即使整体指标不显著，异质性分析也能发现具有正向或负向显著效果的子人群，从而指导产品经理进行有针对性的优化。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "实验异质性（HTE）揭示了同一策略在不同用户群体中可能产生差异化效果。",
      "explanation": "传统平均处理效应（ATE）可能掩盖了子群体的真实行为，而 HTE 通过 CATE 和 ITE 的视角，能更精细地识别用户群体间的异同，为决策提供更准确依据。"
    },
    {
      "point": "异质性分析对于业务迭代和优化具有重要指导意义。",
      "explanation": "通过了解策略对不同用户的效果差异，业务可以深挖背后的原因，找到最优子人群进行重点运营或局部推广，从而提升整体策略效果、减少损失。"
    },
    {
      "point": "京东零售已形成一套自动化的异质性分析工具和实践经验。",
      "explanation": "其 Python 工具包能实现实验数据自动分析、CATE 差异最大化子人群生成、统计检验及可视化输出，极大简化了异质性分析的门槛和效率，并已被证实能发现传统分析无法识别的业务价值。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在实验数据分析的场景中，经常会遇到分析同样的处理效果在不同的用户群体上是否存在显著差异的问题，此时我们可以利用实验异质性的分析方法，对实验结果进行精细化分析，辅助挖掘结果背后的业务逻辑，帮助业务迭代优化。",
    "HTE 的全称为 Heterogeneous Treatment Effects，即异质处理效应，意为实验中同一个 treatment 对不同的实验样本，得到的策略效果可能是不一样的。",
    "尝试寻找策略最优子人群，让整体无效的策略，有机会进行部分先推全；反之依然，让部分负向的策略，减少损失。",
    "对实验结果建模后预测，对线上提供动态的最优人群支持。"
  ],
